ingredients: SUGAR, ENRICHED FLOUR BLEACHED (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), EGGS, WATER, BUTTER, PALM OIL, NONFAT MILK. CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: LEAVENING (BAKING SODA, SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE), DEXTROSE, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SALT, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, EMULSIFIERS (PROPYLENE GLYCOL MONO AND DIESTERS OF FATTY ACIDS, MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, SOY LECITHIN), XANTHAN GUM, SOYBEAN OIL, YELLOW 5, YELLOW 5 LAKE, YELLOW 6, YELLOW 6 LAKE.
